<section id="more-than-the-ai" class="py-24 px-6 bg-paper-1 text-on-paper">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-display text-on-paper text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-3">More than the AI</h2>
    <p class="text-on-paper-soft text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">
      We didn't skip the fundamentals. We just didn't stop there.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Real exercise library</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          Nearly 1,400 exercises with animated demonstrations, so your clients see exactly what
          to do. Add your own exercises with your own videos when the library doesn't have your
          movement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Build it your way</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          The AI writes the program. You change whatever you want, swap exercises, adjust sets
          and reps, restructure the week. Or build one from scratch yourself.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Supersets, circuits, AMRAP, timed work</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          Program the way you actually program. Not just straight sets.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Reusable templates</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          Build a program once, use it again. Stop starting from a blank page for every client.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Progress that's actually tracked</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          Clients log every set. You see their history, their weights, their body metrics, and
          their progress photos in one place.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-on-paper text-lg mb-2">Check-ins and ratings</h3>
        <p class="text-on-paper-soft leading-relaxed">
          Weekly check-ins and post-workout feedback, so you know how it's landing without
          asking.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
